    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Used to describe works produced by the African ethnic group of the same name, inhabiting Swaziland and South Africa. Mahlalela was the name of a formerly independent chiefdom, and of their chief, within the nation of Swaziland. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
